name: Nina Dobrev
description:
A request of @TheEliteChief01.

Nina Dobrev is a Bulgarian/Canadian actress known for her roles in films such as The Perks of Being a Wallflower or The Final Girls.

1500-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings. Most of the dataset was provided by @TheEliteChief01 himself. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
